on third-party sites to better understand how they are received by our users. To do this, we combine data sets (such as user profiles, statistics, market research and analytics data) that tell us how you and other users interact with content and ads. This information allows us to identify common characteristics, e.g. to determine which content is relevant for which target groups. You can find out which information we or the respective partners would like to use on the basis of your consent in the partner list.","name":"Market Research","id":"customcategory-0803c102-27c4-48a1-8658-67a06ff432d6"},"customcategory-9b784073-3863-4a9e-8aba-8f4fe690cd56":{"description":"We and our partners use information about your activities in our online shop and on third party sites (e.g. your interaction with ads or content) as it helps us to improve our products and services and to develop new products and services based on user interactions, type of audience, etc. This purpose does not include developing or improving user profiles and identifiers. This purpose does not include the development or improvement of user profiles and identifiers. You can find out which information we or the respective partners would like to use on the basis of your consent in the partner list.","name":"Product development","id":"customcategory-9b784073-3863-4a9e-8aba-8f4fe690cd56"},"essential":{"description":"We need certain information to provide our online shop securely and reliably. To do this, we monitor and prevent unusual and potentially fraudulent activities (e.g. in relation to advertising, ad clicks by bots) and ensure that systems and processes are working properly and securely (fraud detection and security). In addition, we need certain information to provide you with functions in our online shop such as shopping basket, wish list and similar functions requested by you. For example, we remember which products you have placed in your shopping basket or added to your wish list (shopping basket, wish list and similar functions). You can see which information we or the respective partners use for these purposes in the partner list.","name":"Performance","id":"essential"},"customcategory-a9b4aeab-cd38-4e73-b32c-c5fd2e9f6841":{"description":"For certain services, we need to be able to assign users on our own or on third-party sites, e.g. in order to be able to show you ads for our products on third-party sites. For this purpose, we or our partners assign a pseudonymous ID. In addition, we and our partners can assign you to third-party sites with the help of your pseudonymised e-mail address or telephone number. You can find out which information we or the respective partners would like to use on the basis of your consent in the partner list.","name":"Identification on third party pages","id":"customcategory-a9b4aeab-cd38-4e73-b32c-c5fd2e9f6841"},"customcategory-ef85decb-262f-4699-8895-36f88b3b2dec":{"description":"We and our partners use information to measure how you interact with the ads and content presented to you in our online shop and on third party sites to determine how well they resonate with you. This includes information about whether you clicked on a product, whether you bought it, whether you saw an ad, whether you clicked on it, whether it made you buy a product or visit a website, and so on. This helps us to understand which products we offer that you are interested in and to understand the relevance of advertising campaigns. You can find out which information we or the respective partners would like to use on the basis of your consent in the partner list.","name":"Display and content measurements","id":"customcategory-ef85decb-262f-4699-8895-36f88b3b2dec"}},"services":{"M_EOROGk2Pg9ZR":{"description":"","id":"M_EOROGk2Pg9ZR","legalBasis":[],"name":"ABOUT YOU (Basic Tracking)"},"MMbRBi46puDo2F":{"description":"","id":"MMbRBi46puDo2F","legalBasis":[],"name":"ABOUT YOU (Personalization)"},"w6nfrRum0y3H8O":{"description":"","id":"w6nfrRum0y3H8O","le